    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = v1
    v2 = tmp
    tmp = (v0 + (wp.exp(v1 + 0.11) - wp.exp(v2 + 0.78)))
    v2 = (0.36 + v1)
    v1 = 0.53
    tmp = wp.sin(wp.exp(wp.sin(v1 + 0.16)))
    v0 = 0.70
    v1 = ((v2 * wp.exp(v2 + 0.42)) * (tmp + wp.cos(tmp + 0.84)))
    data[tid] = v0
